title: Deflategate update & around the NFC in 48 minutes
itunes:title: Deflategate update & around the NFC in 48 minutes
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest "Deflategate" news (6:22), La'el Collins signing with the Cowboys (17:35) and discuss the current state of all 16 NFC teams (31:44). Plus, is Ed Reed the NFL's greatest free safety of all time?
